  Welcome to BlazzCore — a minimal, fast, Wayland-first Linux OS.

  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
  │  Desktop      labwc (Wayland compositor)                │
  │  Audio        PipeWire + WirePlumber                    │
  │  Browser      Chromium (GPU-accelerated)                │
  │  Shell        Bash + foot terminal                      │
  │  Packages     pacman (Arch Linux rolling)               │
  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘

  Keyboard shortcuts:
    Super + Enter       Terminal (foot)
    Super + D           App launcher (wofi)
    Super + E           File manager (thunar)
    Super + B           Browser (Chromium)
    Super + V           Clipboard history
    Super + L           Lock screen
    Super + N           Toggle night light
    Super + Shift + P   Power menu
    Super + ,           Settings
    Alt   + Tab         Switch windows
    Print               Screenshot (full screen)
    Shift + Print       Screenshot (select area)
    Ctrl  + Print       Screenshot (to clipboard only)
    Super + Shift + R   Toggle screen recording

  Useful commands:
    blazzcore-settings  Settings GUI
    blazzcore-power     Power menu
    btop                System monitor
    tictactoe           Tic Tac Toe game
    nmtui               Wi-Fi (text UI)
    pacman -Syu         Update all packages

